Version 0 begin:

[h1]Core Mechanisms[/h1]
Battles & Bellies implements many new rules and mechanics to turn enemies into entrees in D&D. The goal of these mechanics is to create a compelling and easy-to-use implementation of vore in D&D.

[h2]Stomach Capacity[/h2]
The amount of food you can store in your belly is limited, and its base value is subject to the size of your character and any other applicable modifiers such as magic items or feats. The amount of space a creature takes up is equivalent to its own base stomach capacity.

