[h3]Maximum Capacity[/h3]
The Maximum Capacity of a creature's belly is twice the listed Belly Capacity.

[h2]Devouring[/h2]
Any creature may make a [b]Devour[/b] attempt as an Action. In order to do so the creature (now referred to as the [b]Pred[/b]) must be within 5 ft of their target (now referred to as the [b]Prey[/b]) and make a contested check that may only benefit from the following modifiers:

[b]The Pred rolls 1d20 + [Size Difference modifier] + [Stomach Capacity modifier][/b]
